{
  "stem": "54.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some people came to visit us, because they had family in Europe, you know-- different cities, you know, in Europe and Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they came see-- to ask us, maybe did you find-- maybe did you see a brother of mine, a sister of mine, or who else?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we didn't know the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They brought us over to the Jewish Federation, and they start doing something for us, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they gave us-- after that, they made in the same building-- they send us in a-- a woman.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was the manager.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they made-- opened up a kitchen for us there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was the cook.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was cooking for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was preparing food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we start already-- living already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was already a bit better than in-- in camp, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then the group-- from the group-- from this group-- the guys, you know, the boys over there, you know, already 25, 26, 30 people-- all 30 years old, you know-- older than that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they start buying cigarettes in Belgium and going back to Germany to sell over there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they didn't have nothing in Germany at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So one day, I said to mine-- to one of-- of the guys, I says, well, you're going to Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll give you a picture of mine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Put down my name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Put down where I'm-- where I'm-- where I have.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, if you go to Germany, if you see somebody, ask-- show them the picture.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe they know somebody-- a sister of mine, or a brother of mine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You never know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Matter of fact, that he came to one of the camps-- in the front of the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in Zeilsheim.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
